# Performance Analyzer - Sitecore Hackathon 2026

## Project Description

**Performance Analyzer** is an application for **SitecoreAI Marketplace** developed for the Sitecore Hackathon 2026. When opened as a side panel in Pages (SitecoreAI Page Builder), it should automatically obtain the HTML of the current page to analyze its performance.

## Technology Stack

| Category | Technology |
|----------|------------|
| Framework | Next.js 16.1.6 (with Turbopack) |
| Language | TypeScript 5.9.3 |
| UI Library | React 19.2.4 |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS 4.1.18 + PostCSS |
| Components | shadcn/ui (base-nova style) |
| UI Primitives | Radix UI |
| Icons | Lucide React, MDI |
| Sitecore SDK | @sitecore-marketplace-sdk/client (0.3.2), @sitecore-marketplace-sdk/xmc (0.4.1) |

